# AI Usage Documentation
## Tools Used
- ChatGPT for making Flask routes, html templates, css styles.
- Gemini for debugging and code review, SQL queries for job match, UI chnages

## Key Prompts
1. "Write a Flask CURD route for companies table with mySQL database connection"
2. "Create an HTML templates for the porject with the requirements that uses css styling"
3. "How to add requirements to job on mySQL so that i can create a job match feature for the project"
## What Worked Well
- AI-generated the basic CRUD routes and html templates quickly
- Able to copy and paste erorr messages and be able to quicky debugg and fix the application.
## What I Modified
- Changed the template provided by the AI to input the variables from my database
- Added the required tables for the job match
- Fixed any errors that I ran into from mistakes in the AI provided templates
## Lessons Learned
- AI is very helpful and faster than any human ever.
- AI work need to be double checked as it also has errors very often
- AI responses are very inconsistant, you have to moitor the output and really pay attention to what you use ai for.
- You are responible of setting up with your own varaible. AI is a good guider, you still need to put the finishing touches.

